{"tid":2076893,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"特朗普簽署行政命令停止向外國人發出工作簽證直至年底","createTime":"2020-06-24T01:36:18.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T12:45:57.000Z","uid":166360,"like":22,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"76aeb19d95a19caec43f170558c7d28ef96be50e","tid":2076893,"uid":166360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:36:18.000Z","msg":"特朗普簽署行政命令停止向外國人發出工作簽證直至年底<br />\n2020-06-24 HKT 02:46<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普以新型肺炎疫情導致經濟不景為由，簽署行政命令，停止向外國人發出工作簽證，直至今年底，以保留工作職位給本土國民，相關命令亦包括暫緩部分親屬移民申請。<br />\n<br />\n(已節錄)<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533744-20200624.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533744-20200624.htm&d=91nyg34XrGq4aGOua7i4Ja0EM2ZTCgB2Df5M2YAuo3Y%3D&h=6fb958d9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1533744-20200624.htm&h=5d464421\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1533744-20200624.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5462a16e438b1de45e45144e634b741ebabae687","tid":2076893,"uid":127575,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:46:51.000Z","msg":"應該為咗保障當地人民"},{"pid":"0e349e67789117156e6c50f52411baf8d952cf38","tid":2076893,"uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5462a16e438b1de45e45144e634b741ebabae687","tid":2076893,"uid":127575,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:46:51.000Z","msg":"應該為咗保障當地人民"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-24T01:48:01.000Z","msg":"當然<br />\n不過對想去美國工作的香港人來說就絕對是壞消息"},{"pid":"0826c8b2a61da5cc381d0fd09386b8e7606eac3e","tid":2076893,"uid":127575,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0e349e67789117156e6c50f52411baf8d952cf38","tid":2076893,"uid":166360,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"5462a16e438b1de45e45144e634b741ebabae687","tid":2076893,"uid":127575,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06